(44, 1, '2017-12-04 18:39:41', '2017-12-04 18:39:41', 'We also provide services of 3D designing, as most of the clients come to us for getting just an idea about their location. we provide many ideas and show them into reality. By having many ideas for the same location is a great chance for them for best utilization of their location with having more useful placing without effecting fashion standards. We strongly follow the standards and set dimensions by our clients.  our cycle for 3d designing is simple.\r\n\r\nwe follow a simple rule: <span style=\"color: #00a86b;\"><strong>Converting Ideas into Reality</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"centerimg aligncenter wp-image-197 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/okasha/wp-content/uploads/ideas-into-Reality.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"795\" height=\"263\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe provide 3D designing services in such a way that you can feel real effect of your place. We have a huge amount of work done in the market and below is an example of our work that shows our expertise.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"centerimg aligncenter wp-image-198 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/okasha/wp-content/uploads/3DRenderingProcess.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe also make the setting for your home, office and other places like businesses areas etc. We also try to make use of huge things in small place so you can take benefits from them, but we don\'t put things in a mess. Below is some work from our past projects that show how we make things easier for you without any hassle.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"centerimg aligncenter wp-image-203 size-large\" src=\"http://localhost/okasha/wp-content/uploads/convert-drawing-into-reality-1024x711.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"711\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"centerimg aligncenter wp-image-202 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/okasha/wp-content/uploads/3d-sample-work.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1240\" height=\"929\" />', 'Services', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'services', '', '', '2018-01-14 16:30:20', '2018-01-14 16:30:20', '', 0, 'http://localhost/okasha/?page_id=44', 0, 'page', '', 0),
